title.S: Menko PMK: Cuti Bersama Idul Fitri Tetap Ada, Tapi Tak Boleh Mudik!

description.S: Pemerintah resmi melarang mudik Lebaran bagi seluruh masyarakat. Namun, Cuti bersama Idul Fitri tetap ada.

gt_title.S: Coordinating Minister PMK: Leave with Eid al-Fitr remains, but it should not be going home!

gt_description.S: The government officially banned Lebaran homecoming for all communities. However, leave with Eid al-Fitr remained.

title.S: Ricuh di Depan PN Jaktim, 4 Simpatisan Rizieq Diamankan

description.S: Massa simpatisan Habib Rizieq Shihab datang ke PN Jaktim. Polisi memberikan imbauan untuk bubar, namun imbauan itu dihiraukan hingga terjadi kericuhan.

gt_title.S: Chaos in front of the East Jakarta District Court, 4 Rizieq sympathizers are secured

gt_description.S: The mass of sympathizers Habib Rizieq Shihab came to the East Jakarta District Court. The police planned to disperse, but the appeal was ignored until there was a riot.

description.S: Tilang elektronik atau e-TLE sudah diterapkan di Jambi. Warga yang melanggar lalu lintas pun sudah diberi surat cinta dari polisi. Lalu apa reaksi mereka?

gt_description.S: Electronic or e-tle tables have been applied in Jambi. Residents who violated traffic had been given a love letter from the police. Then what is their reaction?
